Package com.hannesdorfmann.mosby3

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivityMviDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    A delegate for Activities to attach them to mosbies mvp.
    FragmentMviDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    A delegate for Fragments to attach them to mosby mvp.
    MviDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    Callback that will be called to instantiate the presenter.
    ViewGroupMviDelegate<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    The mvp delegate used for everything that derives from View like FrameLayout etc.
    ViewGroupMviDelegateCallback<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    An enhanced version of MviDelegateCallback that adds support for android.view.ViewGroup like FrameLayout etc.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityMviDelegateImpl<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    The concrete implementation of ActivityMviDelegate.
    FragmentMviDelegateImpl<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    The default implementation of FragmentMviDelegate The View is attached to the Presenter in Fragment#onViewCreated(View, Bundle).
    MosbySavedState
    The SavedState implementation to store the view's internal id to
    PresenterManager
    A internal class responsible to save internal presenter instances during screen orientation changes and reattach the presenter afterwards.
    ViewGroupMviDelegateImpl<V extends MvpView,P extends MviPresenter<V,?>>
    The default implementation of ViewGroupMviDelegate
